were right, Curtis. l was wrong.''

542
00:34:40,920 --> 00:34:42,069
OK, OK, l admit it.

543
00:34:43,560 --> 00:34:45,710
They're happy.
They're working hard.

544
00:34:45,840 --> 00:34:47,717
Everything's going to be fine.

545
