This book is very
interesting reading.

546
00:34:49,840 --> 00:34:52,434
There's a lot of rules
they're not following.

547
00:34:52,560 --> 00:34:54,551
That's what l've been
saying all along.

548
00:34:54,680 --> 00:34:57,831
