- Yes!

569
00:36:05,200 --> 00:36:07,873
- lt's nice to meet you.
- Nice to meet you.

570
00:36:08,360 --> 00:36:10,954
- Here, why don't you sit down?
- Oh, thank you.

571
00:36:11,080 --> 00:36:13,036
Thank you very much.

572
00:36:16,920 --> 00:36:18,831
